day 53 of crew matrix : program that checks if two fractions have the same numerator or denominator:

IN C :
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int num1, denom1, num2, denom2;

    // Input for the first fraction
    printf("Enter the numerator and denominator of the first fraction (e.g., 3 4 for 3/4): ");
    scanf("%d %d", &num1, &denom1);

    // Input for the second fraction
    printf("Enter the numerator and denominator of the second fraction (e.g., 3 6 for 3/6): ");
    scanf("%d %d", &num2, &denom2);

    // Check if the numerators or denominators are the same
    if (num1 == num2 && denom1 == denom2) {
        printf("Both numerators and denominators are the same.\n");
    } else if (num1 == num2) {
        printf("The numerators are the same.\n");
    } else if (denom1 == denom2) {
        printf("The denominators are the same.\n");
    } else {
        printf("Neither the numerators nor the denominators are the same.\n");
    }

    return 0;
}

O/P :
Enter the numerator and denominator of the first fraction (e.g., 3 4 for 3/4): 3 4
Enter the numerator and denominator of the second fraction (e.g., 3 6 for 3/6): 3 6
The numerators are the same.

IN PYTHON:
# Input for the first fraction
num1 = int(input("Enter the numerator of the first fraction: "))
denom1 = int(input("Enter the denominator of the first fraction: "))

# Input for the second fraction
num2 = int(input("Enter the numerator of the second fraction: "))
denom2 = int(input("Enter the denominator of the second fraction: "))

# Check if the numerators or denominators are the same
if num1 == num2 and denom1 == denom2:
    print("Both numerators and denominators are the same.")
elif num1 == num2:
    print("The numerators are the same.")
elif denom1 == denom2:
    print("The denominators are the same.")
else:
    print("Neither the numerators nor the denominators are the same.")

O/P :
Enter the numerator of the first fraction: 3
Enter the denominator of the first fraction: 4
Enter the numerator of the second fraction: 3
Enter the denominator of the second fraction: 6
The numerators are the same.
